function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	Hydra.ActorPlaySound(idAltar, S_SFX_DEMONTAUNT)
	--Knocks player away after shrine is used
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tBossFight) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idSpawner, S_PWR_KNOCKBACK)
		end
	end
	--Plays  fire fx on eyes
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	for i, idFire in pairs(tFires) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFire) then
			Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idFire, 0.5)
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFire, S_FIRESTART)
			Hydra.Wait(0.2)
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idFire, S_FIRE, true)
		end
	end
end

function Start()
	--Spawn Waves
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tOnslaught) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
		end
	end
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	--Stop spawning
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tOnslaught) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, true)
		end
	end

	--Delete the 1" tall mortar cultist R.I.P. buddy :bigbosssalute:
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMortarer) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idMortarer)
	end
end

unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	--Spawns firewall where monsters spawn
	idFirewall = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_FIREWALL, idActorSpawned, false, 0, 0)
	table.insert(tFirewalls, idFirewall)
	Hydra.ActorFaceActor(idFirewall, idSelf, true)
	Hydra.ActorFaceFacing(idFirewall, Hydra.FacingRotate(Hydra.ActorGetFacing(idFirewall), 90), true)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idFirewall, S_PWR_FIREWALL)
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	--Fire mortars on monster death
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMortarer) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorKiller) then
		Hydra.QActorPower(idMortarer, S_MORTAR, idActorKiller)
	end
end

function Start(szGroup)

--Spawn reward chest
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idHeroicChest, false)

	--If the mastery hasn't been completed remove the gem but keep the statue
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGem) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idGem)
	end

	--Delete the statue fire if it hasn't been deleted already.
	for i, idFire in pairs(tFires) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFire) then
			Hydra.ActorDelete(idFire)
		end
	end	
	
	--Delete any fire spawned by enemies.
	for i, idFirewall in ipairs(tFirewalls) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFirewall) then
			Hydra.ActorDelete(idFirewall)
		end
	end

end

unk_9c63f9d.value:
--If mastery succeeded spawn boss
if nVictoryTier == 3 then 
	Hydra.Wait(1)

	--Destroy the altar
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idAltar)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idGem)

	--Remove the fires
	for i, idFire in pairs(tFires) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFire) then
			Hydra.ActorDelete(idFire)
		end
	end

	--Spawn Boss Wave
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tBossFight) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
			Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idAltar, 5)
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idAltar, S_STATUEEXPLODE_PHYSICAL)
			Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idAltar, S_STATUEEXPLODE_FIRE)
		end
	end
end
